Gungame map from [J+J] Server Group. our website: http://jandjservergroup.webs.com
our steamgroup: http://steamcommunity.com/groups/jjsg
Lower Floor: maze with teleport to top in middle
1st floor: maze with teleport to top in middle
Top floor: catwalks with a view on the 1st floor maze

to install, extract the files in the zip to your desktop and then copy them to your "steam/steamapps/user/counter-strike source/cstrike" directory
